## Concept Testing Workflow

- [ ] 1. Define test objectives: What decisions will this test inform?
- [ ] 2. Select concepts to test: 2-4 concepts maximum for clarity
- [ ] 3. Design test instrument: Survey, focus group, or interview guide
- [ ] 4. Recruit participants: Representative of target audience
- [ ] 5. Execute test: Collect feedback systematically
- [ ] 6. Analyze results: Score and synthesize feedback
- [ ] 7. Make recommendation: Which concept(s) to proceed with and why

## Key Inputs
- Concepts to test: {{concepts}}
- Target audience: {{target_audience}}
- Test method: {{test_method}}
- Sample size: {{sample_size}}
